  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an Adventure across time in the land of Fayrehaven!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step backwards in time to the old world of Fayrehaven, a land where trade is your greatest ally. Carve out your path as a savvy trader. Your task is to navigate through different settlements, making shrewd deals and strategic trades to amass wealth and make improvements to your boat and equipment. Decisions that you make impact your fortune and the future of your family back in the present.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rise to the challenge and become the most renowned trader in Fayrehaven’s history. Embrace the family secret of trading across time to help them when they really need it most.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182750/extras/4d0c0861e2667fd2d5473f1521dd4d78.avif?t=1746999659\" width=616 height=316 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Travel, Trade, and Upgrade</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a thrilling journey across nine unique settlements in the old land of Fayrehaven! Master the art of trading by capitalizing on the ever-changing market prices. Use your profits to upgrade your gear, making you a faster and more efficient trader.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182750/extras/4dab1d5975fc98c4d9808097a13f3417.avif?t=1746999659\" width=616 height=216 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore and Search for Lost Cargo</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the mysteries of Fayrehaven Lake, where lost cargo awaits discovery. Can you uncover the rare chest brimming with valuable treasures?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182750/extras/4d6e05673951d60ac24371b943bd76b5.avif?t=1746999659\" width=616 height=216 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Relax and Spend Some Time Fishing on the Lake</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a break from trading and enjoy the serene waters of Fayrehaven Lake. Fishing is not only relaxing but also a great way to earn some extra coins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182750/extras/4bec3b3e9d2ded1efa0ef3ebd339c136.avif?t=1746999659\" width=616 height=216 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Avoid the Thieves on the Lake</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beware of the cunning thieves lurking around Fayrehaven Lake! Outsmart them with your quick thinking or use your stash to hide your valuables.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182750/extras/99e6ff58fdccbb6bca87dfe78968a79c.avif?t=1746999659\" width=616 height=216 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wishlist to be notified on release</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182750/extras/c15d001b4b4b893b212af606014ab7df.avif?t=1746999659\" width=568 height=180 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an Adventure across time in the land of Fayrehaven!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step backwards in time to the old world of Fayrehaven, a land where trade is your greatest ally. Carve out your path as a savvy trader. Your task is to navigate through different settlements, making shrewd deals and strategic trades to amass wealth and make improvements to your boat and equipment. Decisions that you make impact your fortune and the future of your family back in the present.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rise to the challenge and become the most renowned trader in Fayrehaven’s history. Embrace the family secret of trading across time to help them when they really need it most.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182750/extras/4d0c0861e2667fd2d5473f1521dd4d78.avif?t=1746999659\" width=616 height=316 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Travel, Trade, and Upgrade</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a thrilling journey across nine unique settlements in the old land of Fayrehaven! Master the art of trading by capitalizing on the ever-changing market prices. Use your profits to upgrade your gear, making you a faster and more efficient trader.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182750/extras/4dab1d5975fc98c4d9808097a13f3417.avif?t=1746999659\" width=616 height=216 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore and Search for Lost Cargo</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the mysteries of Fayrehaven Lake, where lost cargo awaits discovery. Can you uncover the rare chest brimming with valuable treasures?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182750/extras/4d6e05673951d60ac24371b943bd76b5.avif?t=1746999659\" width=616 height=216 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Relax and Spend Some Time Fishing on the Lake</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a break from trading and enjoy the serene waters of Fayrehaven Lake. Fishing is not only relaxing but also a great way to earn some extra coins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182750/extras/4bec3b3e9d2ded1efa0ef3ebd339c136.avif?t=1746999659\" width=616 height=216 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Avoid the Thieves on the Lake</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beware of the cunning thieves lurking around Fayrehaven Lake! Outsmart them with your quick thinking or use your stash to hide your valuables.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182750/extras/99e6ff58fdccbb6bca87dfe78968a79c.avif?t=1746999659\" width=616 height=216 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wishlist to be notified on release</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182750/extras/c15d001b4b4b893b212af606014ab7df.avif?t=1746999659\" width=568 height=180 /></span></p>",
